name: Quim Coin
description: Quim Coin is a Social Fan Token based on the BEP20 Smart Chain oriented for the Portuguese Community Worldwide. A Fan Club that supports the Popular Artist/Entertainer Quim Barreiros. All the Crypto raised in the token sale will give it's holders access to this artist's NFT's which are being developed in a parallel project. the NFT's will be minted on BEP721 Smart Chain.
